- Choose/fork blockchain platform
- Set up node infrastructure
- Build basic vote recording system
- Create UN data import pipeline
- Historical vote database

**Core App:**
- Web application (responsive)
- Basic voting interface
- User authentication (privacy-preserving)
- Simple visualization
- Vote recording on blockchain

### Phase 2: Enhancement (Months 4-6)

**Biometric Integration:**
- API connections to wearable devices
- Real-time coherence calculation
- Color state algorithm development
- Privacy-preserving data handling
- Opt-in consent flows

**Visualization:**
- Global map interface
- Color gradient system
- Real-time update animations
- Regional aggregation
- Basic temporal views

### Phase 3: Wisdom Layer (Months 7-9)

**Whisper System:**
- Gold vote detection
- Text input interface
- Whisper display algorithm
- Archive and search
- Resonance metrics

**Advanced Visualization:**
- 3D globe rendering
- Whisper flow animations
- Temporal evolution playback
- Comparison matrices
- Export and sharing tools

### Phase 4: Community (Months 10-12)

**Social Features:**
- Discussion forums
- User profiles (anonymous but persistent)
- Following and notification system
- Educational content delivery
- Community guidelines and moderation

**Mobile Apps:**
- iOS native app
- Android native app
- Optimized for on-the-go voting
- Push notifications for key votes
- Offline capability with sync

### Phase 5: Scale & Refine (Year 2+)

**Global Expansion:**
- Multilingual support
- Regional servers for speed
- Partnership with NGOs
- Academic research collaborations
- Media and press outreach

**Advanced Features:**
- AI-assisted summaries of resolutions
- Predictive analytics (will vote pass?)
- Impact tracking (what happened after?)
- Integration with other democratic tools
- API for researchers and developers

